i%C3%AAu-Th%E1%BA%A7n/Ti%E1%BB%83u-th%C3%B4n/poem-RvjVjRNTqIAv-7N3ia27rA">Tiểu thôn - 小村</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Mai-Nghi%C3%AAu-Th%E1%BA%A7n/author-LM0kb8TnwF3pXyZ2viD2Eg">Mai Nghiêu Thần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/V%C4%83n-t%E1%BA%BF-th%E1%BA%A7n-s%C3%A1ch/poem-jodinZfi6gur7Teb7mLN4w">Văn tế thần sách - 祭書神文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Vi%C3%AAn-h%E1%BB%AFu-%C4%91%C3%A0o-2/poem-xXXmebwE7TXR0DqL9FlYyQ">Viên hữu đào 2 - 園有桃 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-V/poem-66hY9e29sguyjetp3Y8QFg">Vô đề (V) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-VNhahLxtqyIrLeDASL0s9Q">Thực Hiền</a>)<br></div>	</div>
